{'id': 7216157, 'body': 'Hi,
The tree in Forest only withers when you "leave the app". Please make sure you do not press the home button unintentionally when you lock/unlock the screen so that your tree will not wither. As well, your time will not break up even if you unlock the screen to see how much time is left in Forest. We hope this is clear for you and kindly ask for your understanding. 

Currently, the first tree species purchase will cost 500 coins. Every additional tree species purchase will increase the cost by 100 coins, with the limit set at 1000 coins. Thanks for the feedback and we will further improve Forest overtime! Feel free to contact us via our in-app feedback system if you have further questions or suggestions! :) Forest', 'modified': '2019-02-09T03:24:48Z'}

{'id': 4585893, 'body': 'Hello,

